dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field 2. Fixed spacing error in Admin1 name "Región de Aysén del Gral.Ibañez del Campo" 3. Fixed multipart sliver errors 4. Fixed 1,314 gap errors
